8. Form check: Lock the lats and keep the bar close to the body throughout the pull.
9. The Barbell Clean And Jerk mainly trains your Quadriceps (Quadriceps Femoris), Glutes (gluteus maximus, gluteus mideus), Shoulders (Deltoids). If you are newer to it, start light and add load only once the movement feels controlled, and on heavier sets end the set when your form or brace breaks down rather than grinding out a risky rep.$instr$ WHERE id = 'a569ad67-787a-48de-b5bf-7a8a37dd587a';

